{"tid":1743303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果投泛民無用，點解呢幾日唔攪大佢，等佢取消","createTime":"2019-11-21T06:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:47:43.000Z","uid":52265,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8f2582ebcbf40229981e90357c80e8c29af583","tid":1743303,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"橫掂建制會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164afd7d61b1dcd05ca2dc763d804ff9895b0150","tid":1743303,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=52b811f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=2ab13a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=357f9e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOL